{"tid":16679,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/PS4/XB1] Tom Clancy's The Division 討論區","createTime":"2016-12-01T14:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T07:39:01.000Z","uid":29738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba2c5c20e51a4dff912a9833235285d1ed092e9","tid":16679,"uid":29738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"英文官網：<a href=\"http://tomclancy-thedivision.ubi.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftomclancy-thedivision.ubi.com%2F&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=51888097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tomclancy-thedivision.ubi.com/</a> <br />\n<br />\n正體中文官網：<a href=\"http://www.ubisoft.com.tw/tctd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ubisoft.com.tw%2Ftctd%2F&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=f214e2dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ubisoft.com.tw/tctd/</a> <br />\n<br />\n《湯姆克蘭西：全境封鎖》（Tom Clancy's The Division）是一款第三人稱戰術射擊動作角色扮演遊戲，由Ubisoft Massive、Ubisoft Reflections和Ubisoft Red Storm共同開發，屬於湯姆&middot;克蘭西系列品牌遊戲，將支援Microsoft Windows、PlayStation 4和Xbox One平台。 <br />\n<br />\n《The Division》的故事取材於暗冬行動和第51號總統指令。遊戲中一場在黑色星期五購物季期間散布的疾病，讓美國在五天之內崩解癱瘓。玩者扮演的角色隸屬於一個名為「策略國土部門」（Strategic Homeland Division）的組織，簡稱「The Division」。該組織的目的是要擊退威脅，並儘一切手段來「保存剩下的事物」，並逐步逼近幕後黑手。遊戲中玩者將面臨來自線上其他玩家、電腦（AI）和朋友的挑戰。"},{"pid":"308c54bc7868a34dabf0e8157e4155c077f63cf3","tid":16679,"uid":12399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"Underground 之後無玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS4"},{"pid":"74177a53bdb45537f09a6045249f1b4dba59de7e","tid":16679,"uid":29738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Underground 之後無玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS4</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1.5好似搞得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces